OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FCardiff Council has confirmed there is
OL,7,Fno provision for people whose postal
OL,8,Fballot was delayed, and are now away
OL,9,Ffrom home for the Senedd Election.
OL,11,FIt comes after some voters in Caerdydd
OL,12,FFynnon Taf and Caerdydd Penarth
OL,13,Fconstituencies reported that they had
OL,14,Fnot received their postal vote packs.
OL,16,FThe council confirmed the missing
OL,17,F1,388 packs have now been delivered
OL,18,Fbut some who applied for postal votes
OL,19,Fmay already be away and unable to vote.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
