PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FA council spokesperson said despite
OL,7,Fproviding the necessary data to their
OL,8,Fcontracted print provider, the print
OL,9,Frun intended for last week "did not
OL,10,Ffully take place."
OL,12,FCivica - the print provider - has not
OL,13,Fgiven a reason for the delay to the
OL,14,Fprint run.
OL,16,FOutstanding postal packs have now been
OL,17,Fdelivered by hand by Cardiff Council
OL,18,Fstaff. Voters who are at home can
OL,19,Feither return the packs to polling
OL,20,Fstations, community hubs or County
OL,21,FHall on Wednesday and Thursday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FCardiff Council added: "Unfortunately,
OL,7,Ffor those now away from home, there is
OL,8,Fno provision at this stage to cancel
OL,9,Fan existing postal vote arrangement in
OL,10,Forder to apply for an emergency proxy.
OL,12,F"The Council regrets the inconvenience
OL,13,Fexperienced by those affected and
OL,14,Fremains fully focused on ensuring that
OL,15,Fthe election is conducted effectively
OL,16,Fand in accordance with all Electoral
OL,17,FCommission requirements."
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
