OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FBut voters can only apply for an
OL,7,Femergency proxy if something prevents
OL,8,Fthem from voting that they were not
OL,9,Fpreviously aware of, such as a medical
OL,10,Femergency or being away for work.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Conservatives have responded
OL,13,Fto the delays, stating that those who
OL,14,Fapplied for a postal vote "should not
OL,15,Fbe left wondering whether they will be
OL,16,Fable to cast their ballot at all."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FA spokesperson added: "Given Royal
OL,7,FMail's statement, serious questions
OL,8,Fnow need to be answered by the Labour-
OL,9,Frun Cardiff Council about how this
OL,10,Ffailure happened, how many voters were
OL,11,Faffected, and why these ballot packs
OL,12,Fwere apparently never printed in the
OL,13,Ffirst place. Public confidence in
OL,14,Felections is vital, and this Labour
OL,15,Fadministration must be fully
OL,16,Ftransparent about what has gone wrong."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FIn response, a Welsh Labour
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "It is extremely
OL,8,Fconcerning that some of those
OL,9,Fregistered for a postal vote in the
OL,10,FCardiff seats are yet to receive them.
OL,11,FThis means that many could be denied
OL,12,Fthe chance to vote in this election.
OL,14,F"The council is taking action, but
OL,15,Fthis must include ensuring that
OL,16,Fballots are returned in good time to
OL,17,Fbe counted. Anything that interferes
OL,18,Fin the democratic process at this late
OL,19,Fstage is obviously a major issue for
OL,20,Fany party."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
