PN,46809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson commented:
OL,7,F"It is extremely worrying that so many
OL,8,Fvoters haven't received their postal
OL,9,Fvote packs due to a printing error.
OL,10,FAlthough emergency measures were put
OL,11,Fin place to reach as many constituents
OL,12,Fas possible, it is inevitable that
OL,13,Fmany will lose their vote.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778193329
OL,3,CPrinting delay leaves some unable to
OL,4,Cvote in Senedd Election
OL,6,F"Under the new electoral system, every
OL,7,Fvote counts and even a small number of
OL,8,Fmissing ballots could make a real
OL,9,Fdifference, especially in very
OL,10,Fmarginal areas, in who forms the next
OL,11,FWelsh Government. Plaid Cymru is
OL,12,Furging anyone who has not received
OL,13,Ftheir postal vote pack to contact
OL,14,Ftheir local council immediately."
OL,16,FReform UK added: "This is totally
OL,17,Funacceptable. While we think there are
OL,18,Ftoo many people using postal votes
OL,19,Fgenerally, people who have signed up
OL,20,Fto vote by post in good faith should
OL,21,Fnot be disenfranchised."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
